{
  "stem": "428.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they had-- while I was working during the day, at night, the water used to come in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they used to have a water pump what was running the whole night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to take care of that water pump the whole night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I used to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I used to come only in the camp to get some food and clothes, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then in 1942, they liquidated that camp, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took us into the regular concentration camp-- Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They used to call it Jerozolimska.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And over there, it was that professional killer, Goth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Goth.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And over there, I used to work also as a blacksmith.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I used to take care-- they have mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What they exploding those mountains and they have a compressor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I used to work by that compressor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then after working there-- it was-- it was terrible because for nothing they kill you there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For instance, he went--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For instance, you walk and he calls you-- come on, come over here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I came to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he tells me, look in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you couldn't look such a bastard in the eyes, so you look away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he tells you, [SPEAKING GERMAN] You don't have a clear conscience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Boom.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He kill you for this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then a girl was carrying stones in a carriage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Such a carriage what they carry--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she saw him walking, so she put on full.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that stones, when she was carrying that, the stones used to fall down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he says, you're making sabotage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he kill her for this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then it was-- then was times-- for instance, I was very short of being killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
